item.title: About
item.description: Hello, I’m Jiayee. I’m currently working as a software engineer at Indeed. I graduated from NUS Computer Science in 2019. Through blogging, I hope to be better at retaining what I learnt. Please keep in mind that not everything in this blog is correct. I am and will always be learning. Resume (last updated on 10 Sep 2020)
